Feature: Successful flow
    We enqueue my PRs one by one and everything goes well.

    Scenario: Merging one PR
        Given PR 1 exists

        When Flow starts
        Then No markers exist except PR branch

        When PR 1 is enqueued
        Then Push was called 1 time
        #    , for queue
        And Some new markers appear
        And Source and rebase match original branch
        #   , because branch does not move for PR that is already on top
        And Source and rebase match original branch
        And Merge-after-rebase matches new queue head
        And Main does not match queue

        When PR 1 is merged
        Then Push was called 2 times
        #    , for pr branch and for main
        And Markers disappear together with original branch
        And Main now matches queue
